# 💼 AI Resume Screening Chatbot (RAG-based)

An intelligent **Resume Screening System** that uses **Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)** to filter and rank resumes based on user requirements through a chatbot interface.

This project simulates a **recruiter assistant**, allowing users to input job requirements and get the most relevant candidates with explanations.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📄 Upload and process multiple resume PDFs
- 🧠 Semantic search using embeddings
- 🔍 Fast retrieval using FAISS vector database
- 🤖 Chatbot interface for natural language queries
- 📊 Candidate ranking based on relevance
- 🧾 Context-aware answers using LLM (Groq / OpenAI compatible)

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

User Query
↓
Embedding Generation
↓
FAISS Vector Search (Top K resumes)
↓
LLM (Context + Query)
↓
Ranked Candidates + Explanation


---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Backend
- Python

### AI / NLP
- Sentence Transformers (embeddings)
- LLM (Groq / OpenAI API)

### Vector Database
- FAISS

### Document Processing
- LangChain (PDF Loader, Text Splitter)

### Frontend
- Streamlit

---

## 📂 Project Structure

resume-screening/
│── data/ # Resume PDFs
│── vectorstore/ # FAISS index
│── app.py # Streamlit UI
│── rag.py # Retrieval + LLM logic
│── parser.py # PDF loading
│── embedder.py # Embedding model
│── requirements.txt
│── .env
│── README.md

